summary:
I am a highly motivated individual with a drive for personal excellence. I work well as an individual, efficiently completing tasks within the stipulated time. I also work well within a team, adapting effortlessly into the role of leadership or compliance when necessary. My goal is to enhance the team within your company and be a valuable asset to my company. 

My education is well rounded within Business as well as Clinical.  These two can be merged to fully execute my job potential and qualifications. However, my preference is, but not limited to, the Business, Marketing field. My personal goal is to further my tertiary education in business and marketing for my professional development. To continously grow and apply those soft skills so very needed in any business relationship today.
